Do’s
- Maintain a professional and respectful tone in posts and comments
- Verify information before sharing it
- Use strong privacy settings to protect personal data
- Build a positive digital footprint 
- Think before posting

Don’ts
- Do not share sensitive personal or financial information
- Avoid posting offensive, inappropriate, or harmful content
- Do not engage in cyberbullying or online harassment
- Avoid spreading misinformation or unverified news
- Do not mix overly casual behavior with professional platforms
